invalid type: string "- Jump Rope (HIIT style) - 3x60s\nFitness & Recovery Tips:\n- Train with moderate to heavy weights for muscle tone and fat burn.\n- Limit rest between sets (30-60 seconds) for higher intensity.\n- Walk at least 10,000 steps daily.\n- Drink 3-4 liters of water daily.\n- Ensure 7-8 hours of sleep for proper recovery.\nel Rollouts - 3x10\n\nnow and ice  32 \naining  48 \nn \n \n